# Desktop (Wails) frontend build artifacts. The embedded dist/ is checked in so
# `//go:embed all:frontend/dist` resolves without a separate npm build, so it is
# force-un-ignored against the global dist/ rule above.
desktop/frontend/node_modules
desktop/frontend/build/
desktop/build/bin/
# Wails generates this dev-mode variant of Info.plist at build time.
desktop/build/darwin/Info.dev.plist
# Wails regenerates these on every `wails build`; the frontend talks to the
# bindings via window.go directly, so the generated copies are not source.
desktop/frontend/wailsjs/
desktop/frontend/package.json.md5
!desktop/frontend/dist/
!desktop/frontend/dist/**
